&lt;p&gt;Your next opportunity awaits! Fletcher Jones Motorcars, a leading automotive dealership, is seeking motivated individuals to join our team as an Apprentice Technicians. As an Apprentice Technician you will have the opportunity to learn and develop your skills in a fast-paced and dynamic environment. You will work alongside experience technicians and receive comprehensive training to become a proficient automotive technician.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automotive Technicians – we’ve got your covered! &lt;/strong&gt;We offer free health insurance for you and your family, paid training, competitive hourly rates and a busy shop – maximize your productivity and maximize your earnings! &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize diagnostic tools and equipment to accurately diagnose mechanical and electrical malfunction of vehicles and perform repairs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accurately document record of all repairs, services and maintenance performed on vehicles in accordance with dealership and manufacturer standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with service team to ensure efficient workflow and timely completion of repairs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform maintenance and repairs with efficiency and in accordance with dealership and manufacturer standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Valid driver’s license and clean driving record&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Degree or Certificate from a trade school preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience as an automotive technician preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dental insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vision insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid time off&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401(k)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401(k) matching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible spending account&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional development assistance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Life insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee assistance plan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Disability insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pay: $18 - $18 / hour&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;At Fletcher Jones Motorcars, we attract, nurture, and retain the most talented people in the industry by providing the highest quality work environment where productivity, creativity, and personal and professional growth can flourish. We believe our team sits behind the wheel of the Fletcher Jones brand that drives our company toward success.&lt;/p&gt;
