&lt;p&gt;At Fletcher Jones Motorcars, our mission is to deliver a world class guest experience through the pursuit of excellence. It is this journey, fueled by innovation and integrity, that has led us to be a part of the nation’s #1 family-owned automotive group. We are seeking a Sales Consultant to join our team.&lt;/p&gt;
